value.string: A most unusual property that has development possibilities. Located directly across the street from the renowned surf spot, "Big Left", the large yard has an imu for your family luau. Two buildings have rental potential on half an acre. Views of Kahului harbor and majestic Haleakala where you can view beautiful sunrises, can be seen from the property. Open parking area has plenty of room for residents and guests. Centrally located in Wailuku and just a short distance from grocery shopping, banking and restaurants. Kahului Airport is only 15 minutes away. Make this special property into that of which you have been dreaming. Add a second story and a view of the ocean could open up before you. Building permits were obtained for structures.

Large Maui Meadows lot over 1/2 acres with Ocean Views. 2 bedroom 1 3/4 bath detached ohana on property for rental income or to live in while you build your dream home on the top of the lot. Ohana has vaulted ceilings and very private.

Over 1.5 acres in North Kihei - need I say more??? This property has potential galore and the possibilities are endless! Build your perfect family compound? Residential Condo? Or possibly subdivide and develop like neighboring parcels. The house is in original condition and is uninhabitable in its current condition - the value of this listing is in the land.

This is a great opportunity for you to own within the highly desired Akolea at Kehalani. This single level 3 bedroom 2 bath home is located on a corner lot providing ample views of the West Maui Mountains and Kahului Harbor. Front Load HE washer and dryer, range, and refrigerator included with the sale of the home. Close proximity to schools, shopping and Wailuku Town this is a great home for a growing family.

Here is a special Kihei property that is more than meets the eye. It is located at Makai Heights which is centrally located. It is just minutes to Kahului, the airport and every convenience you need. The lot is a spacious half acre and a rarity at this price. The property has its own well for irrigation. If you like greenery in your environment, this well is golden. The solidly built house is masonry and in good condition for its age. The well thought out built-ins are added value. The cottage is well separated from the main house and very private. Sitting in the carport is like sitting in an outdoor extension of the living area. It is so pleasant with cooling breezes even on a warm day. This property is in the process of being vacated, cleared out and cleaned up.

4 bedroom 3 bath tri level fixer home on the Pukalani Golf Course. Central valley and golf course views from many rooms. This is a bright and airy house with 3 bedrooms 2 baths upstairs and 1 bedroom and a bath on lower level. Flexible floor plan offers multi use rooms. Short sale was recently approved by the bank. New buyer will have to be re-approved.

What are the ingredients for a enticing tropical hideaway? Ocean views; lush grounds; a secluded pool, a cute, a custom cottage and a few pleasant surprises. The two bedroom, two bath cottage features extra-tall fir ceilings, saltillo tile floors, custom Koa wood cabinets and a sweet covered lanai that provides riveting views over the jungle and out to the ocean. Bamboo, palms, plumeria, banana and papaya are just a few of the tropical treats. The location is convenient to shops, restaurants and beaches on the North Shore and more. All furnishings may be purchased via a separate bill of sale.

A Charming Kula Home with open floor plan, high ceilings, plus office and a wood burning stove for those crisp Kula nights. The home has just been completely repainted inside and out. House is build to accommodate a Family of any size~ It boasts a grand Master Suite with large Master bath along with a walk in closet and your own private lanai. Enjoy partial ocean views and beautiful sunsets from your lanai. Home is currently Tenant occupied will need 48hrs to show. Please Do Not Disturb Tenants. Call your favorite Realtor to set up a showing.

Space, Space, Space!!! Come and see this extensively renovated and remodeled house that makes it the most beautiful house in the Waimahaihai Subdivision in Kihei. New additions include new porch, spacious open living areas behind the garage with private bath, extension of the living room and extended space for laundry and bedrooms at the back of the house. The new addition behind the garage allows a flexible floor plan that could be used as a master suite with master bathroom or a separate living quarters with side entrance for extended family members. Another bedroom with a private bathroom can also be used as a second master bedroom. The living room and kitchen allows an open floor plan with island cabinet and granite counter top. New bedroom carpets, new laminated wood floors in the kitchen and living room, new tiles, granite counter tops and solid wood cabinets through out, new paint inside and out, new sliding windows and appliances. New stucco plaster on the main house exterior. New garage door. Roof on the existing structures which was installed in prior years still looks new to match the roof for the new structure additions. New private cottage with new solar water heater. Play with your dog on a spacious backyard behind the main house and cottage. Main house electric meter is upgraded to 200 amps; cottage has separate 100 amps electric meter. Throw your best offer.

This 3 Bedroom 1.5 Bath home is located in the old Koa Subdivision in Wailuku, Zoned R-2. This single story hollow tile home in it's original condition sits on 16,441 sq. ft. The existing lot size allows for a second dwelling. The home is in a great central Maui location, close to everything. It has a huge backyard with a mango tree, avocado and lemon trees.
Conveniently located above Lahaina town, this 10 bedroom 5.5 bath home is perfect for large families or investors. Second floor deck offers ocean views and views of Lahaina town.

House to be built in the desirable upcountry Kula neighborhood of Kulamanu Estates takes advantage of panoramic views. This efficient 3 bedroom 2 bath home of 1206sf with a deck and 500sf garage can be customized into a sweet charmer. Everything needed to enjoy fresh Kula living and easily expandable now or in the future. Fully insulated, thermal dual pane windows and allowances to customize finishes. Protective covenants. To be sold as house and lot package. Home to be built exclusively by Ridgeline Homes, Inc.

SINGLE STORY... Like NEW home in one of Maui's most sought after neighborhoods!!! Renovated in 2015 with new appliances, flooring, bathrooms, plumbing & lighting fixtures, interior/exterior paint, updated automatic sprinkler system, fence gates, 2 wall A/C's, and more... Enjoy indoor/outdoor lifestyle in this 3BD/2Ba North facing home. Large yard with beautifully trimmed tree umbrellas over a large deck area for year round BBQ's and outdoor family fun! Enjoy bird watching, gardening or just relaxing in your beautiful Maui home not far from famous Kam III Beach in South Maui. Open floorplan gives light and shady views from every room. New roof in 2004.

Price Reduction to $699,000! Bring Offers! Privacy~Seclusion behind the gated driveway. Located within a very short walk to a sandy beach on Maui. This centrally air conditioned home with Photo Voltaic panels and solar water heater has a gated entry to a private lush verdant yard with flowering plumerias, bananas and citrus trees. Two story home has an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings. The master bedroom has its own Juliette balcony to have your morning coffee or wind down the day mesmerized by our gorgeous sunset lit sky. Master bedroom has en-suite master bath with double vanity. This property is a private fenced flag lot which offers a long driveway with wooden gate. The foliage creates a sense of a secluded oasis. Original Developer Lot chart allows this large lot to have attached accessory dwelling- so the potential is great! Extra Concrete for more parking in driveway. Located in an established, desirable neighborhood and centrally located to many amenities such a golf, shopping and of course beaches! Listing agent is related to seller. Seller has active Real Estate License in Hawaii and New York. Call your realtor today for your showing!

Spectacular West Maui Mountain and ocean views could be yours! The main dwelling was just completed in 2014 and supplied with stainless steel and gas appliances, custom cabinets with granite counter tops and a solar water heater. This custom 9' ceiling home is a beauty! With a 13' ceiling height in the garage there is plenty room for storage. A plus to this is the cute accessory dwelling that was recently renovated on this large residential property (18,050 sf). Situated at the end of a private road off of Old Haleakala Highway makes this property ideal. Close enough to walk (or drive) to shops and restaurants but tucked away from the busy street(s).

Lovely all useable 1/2 acre view lot with beautiful bi-coastal views plus detached cottage. The property is conveniently located close to the Pukalani Community Center, shopping and schools. Both the main house and cottage interior and exteriors were recently painted. The main house has all new appliances, carpeting, window treatments, garage door plus a new septic system. Must see to appreciate all that has been done.

2 bd, 1 ba house with 1 bd, 1 ba detached rental or in-law cottage (ohana) on 11,375 sq ft lot. $689,000 Beautiful front garden. Lots of light. Gigantic deck overlooking lush green gulch. Detached garage, storage shed. New kitchen counters, recently repaired and painted deck, new refrigerator and washer/dryer in ohana. Views of Maalaea Bay and Haleakala peak from front yard.

Outdoor living at it’s best with a 440 sq. ft. upper deck to entertain guests, enjoy ocean views for whale watching and watch the stunning Maui sunsets to complete the day. This home lives larger than it’s square footage with three bedrooms and two bathrooms leading onto another covered 440 sq. ft lanai perfect for dining, entertaining guests or just to enjoy the back yard with it’s own beauty of flowers and palms. Very usable back yard with enough space to add a pool if that’s on your dream list. Living room and master bedroom has expansive vaulted ceilings. The home has double D glass doors and windows throughout. Four Fujitsu Ductless Air Conditioning units with individual controls throughout the home. Please plan to spend extra time while viewing this home to see why it lives large and is so very comfortable.

Brand new built in 2015, new appliances Must see to appreciate this beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath, 1700 square feet home with 2 car garage. Convenient location in established neighborhood in central Kihei. Close to great shopping, beaches, school and all amenities you are searching for. Newly paved driveway on this large 10,000 square foot lot. As added bonus there is a remodeled (2015) separate 2 BD & 1 bath spacious Ohana toward the back of the property. Very cute! Great rental. Easy to show

Enjoy single level living in this well maintained, ENERGY EFFICIENT, 4 bedroom(one wall was removed to enlarge the Master), 3 bath, remodeled home located on a cul-de-sac in the Piilani Village 1 Subdivision. This inviting home includes numerous upgrades including, 32 photo-voltaic panels that are owned (not leased), 6 split system Air Conditioning units to keep everyone cool, “in wall” wired data and internet installed in every room but the bathrooms, On Demand hot water, a Viking Gas Range with a pot filler faucet for your water filling convenience. Also a Viking Warming Drawer, GE Profile stainless steel appliances, slow close specialty cabinets and drawers, granite counter tops, a granite island, and marble tiled kitchen floors. Wood floors grace the living room and bedrooms. The fully fenced front and back yards have an automated irrigation system along with a back yard lanai for outdoor dining. A storage shed is here for your yard supplies. Piilani Village 1 is conveniently located near the Kihei Community Center and Pool, Piilani Shopping Village and the beaches of South Maui.
